Class AbstractState

  • java.lang.Object
    • chat.common.AbstractState
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    State, State

    public abstract class AbstractState
extends Object
    This abstract class defines the type for a state of a client or a server. The state is the first part of the context for the execution of actions (of algorithms): see the method Action.execute(AbstractState, AbstractContent).
